    "name": "Eyes That Hypnotise",
    "steam_appid": 3156370,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🐾 <strong>手绘温馨益智游戏！</strong> 🐾<br>发现可爱的小动物，把它们合理地摆放到网格上，并沉浸在它们的迷人眼神中吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156370/extras/998a8da883e304a1438981542e8e3bb5.poster.avif?t=1771093721\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156370/extras/998a8da883e304a1438981542e8e3bb5.webm?t=1771093721\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156370/extras/998a8da883e304a1438981542e8e3bb5.mp4?t=1771093721\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🐾 <strong>一款充满温馨氛围的益智游戏，拥有毛茸茸、大眼睛的小动物们！</strong> 🐾</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在 <strong>《Eyes That Hypnotise》</strong> 中，找到每个可爱动物的完美位置，享受幽默有趣的互动，并在轻松的氛围中解开精心设计的谜题。小动物们的眼睛会跟随你的光标，创造出搞笑又呆萌的表情！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✨ <strong>它们的催眠般的眼神会帮助你解谜……还是让你完全分心？</strong> ✨</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156370/extras/b6ce1ad39ee3793310510330fecbb5ff.poster.avif?t=1771093721\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156370/extras/b6ce1ad39ee3793310510330fecbb5ff.webm?t=1771093721\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156370/extras/b6ce1ad39ee3793310510330fecbb5ff.mp4?t=1771093721\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🧩 <strong>游戏特色</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🧠 <strong>96 个精心设计的关卡</strong> <br>每个谜题都经过精心打磨，让你在轻松愉悦的氛围中挑战你的思维。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🌎 <strong>8 大独特章节</strong> <br>探索 <strong>家园、城市、农场、森林、异域</strong> 等温馨场景，每个都有独特的动物和精美背景。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🦉 <strong>30 种大眼睛、充满个性的动物</strong><br>从 <strong>高傲的灵缇犬（Borzoi）到狡猾的小老鼠</strong>，收集各种幽默可爱的生物，每个都有自己的特点！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >👀 <strong>搞笑有趣的互动眼神</strong><br>动物们的眼睛会 <strong>跟随你的光标移动</strong>，让你创造各种搞怪表情。当你解开谜题时——<strong>它们的眼睛会闪闪发光，充满喜悦！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156370/extras/dbab60e4684e064459b5f30d90051b5c.poster.avif?t=1771093721\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156370/extras/dbab60e4684e064459b5f30d90051b5c.webm?t=1771093721\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156370/extras/dbab60e4684e064459b5f30d90051b5c.mp4?t=1771093721\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >📖 <strong>动物收藏册</strong><br>解锁并收集所有可爱的小动物，在你的 <strong>收藏册</strong> 中随时欣赏它们！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🧠 <strong>每个谜题都拥有多种解法</strong><br>自由发挥创意！每道谜题都有 <strong>多种可能的解决方案</strong>，让你可以探索不同的方法。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >💡 <strong>贴心提示系统，不剧透也能帮你前进</strong><br>卡住了吗？别担心！<strong>提示系统会温和地引导你，而不会直接给出答案，让你保留解谜的乐趣。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156370/extras/90197925b2a77bd4abc065e2859142da.poster.avif?t=1771093721\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156370/extras/90197925b2a77bd4abc065e2859142da.webm?t=1771093721\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156370/extras/90197925b2a77bd4abc065e2859142da.mp4?t=1771093721\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🖌 <strong>精美手绘艺术 &amp; 动画</strong><br>每只动物都是 <strong>手工绘制并赋予生动的动画</strong>，展现独特的个性。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎶 <strong>舒缓的音乐 &amp; 温馨音效</strong><br>沉浸在 <strong>悠扬的爵士配乐</strong> 中，让解谜过程更加放松惬意。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >📔 <strong>手账风格的温馨界面</strong><br>游戏的 UI <strong>采用手工笔记本风格</strong>，增加了一种温暖的亲切感。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >😆 <strong>幽默风趣，轻松愉悦</strong><br>调皮地玩弄动物们的眼睛，收集所有可爱的生物，享受美妙的音乐，最重要的是——<strong>尽情享受游戏的乐趣！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
